OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be warm again. A quite
OL,6,Fcloudy morning with patchy drizzle in
OL,7,Fthe west.
OL,8,
OL,9,CTonight:FRain spreads northeast
OL,10,Fthrough the evening and overnight,
OL,11,Fheavy for a time. Then becoming dry
OL,12,Fwith clear spells by morning.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSaturday:FIt will be dry and warm
OL,15,Fthrough the day with some prolonged
OL,16,Fbright or sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
