OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FWarm
OL,6,Ffrom Sunday to Tuesday with plenty of
OL,7,Fbright or sunny spells in the east,
OL,8,Fcloudier at times in the west on
OL,9,FSunday. Perhaps a bit cloudier on
OL,10,FTuesday.
